skins.name: Default
skins.secIdle1Text: Don't you have anything to say? I'm not great at starting conversations...
skins.secIdle2Text: Oh, you want to know about my eyes? One of them is fake... Can you guess which?
skins.secTouchText: Mmm... I don't hate this feeling...
skins.secSpecialTouchText: Are you interested in shut-in girls?

skins.name: Retrofit
skins.secIdle1Text: Mmh... just staying together quietly like this... might be pretty nice too.
skins.secIdle2Text: Wear my clothes properly? Eh...? Don't wanna~ More importantly, care for an Oxy Cola, Commander?
